gold_translation: Anyone who's going to drive at high latitudes or over mountain passes should consider the possibility of snow, ice, or freezing temperatures.

whisper_s_ft: gìnì àjò ìwádí jẹ́ pàtàkì nínú ìsẹ̀ yàrá ìkàwé lọ pọ̀ ìgbà olùkọ́ má ń ní ànfàní láti kú àwọn akẹ́ẹ́kọ́ rẹ̀ lọ sàwọn ibùdó tí wíwọ́ ọkọ̀ kò ní jẹ́ alálẹ̀
nllb_translation: The movement of people is important in the classroom. Most of the time, teachers don't have the opportunity to die.
gold_translation: Field trips are a large part of any classroom. Quite often a teacher would love to take her students places to which a bus trip is not an option.

whisper_s_ft: ìtakún ayélujára se àgbájọ ìbára ẹni sọ̀rọ gbogbogbò àti aládàni
nllb_translation: Internet addiction has made social media a popular and private conversation
gold_translation: The Internet combines elements of both mass and interpersonal communication.
